post_survey.habit_change: i started to listen to a lot of pop punk/punk rock in high school and i still listen to it now, but i listen to a lot of different types of rock in general. I don't listen to as much hip hop because i don't listen to radio as much or go to clubs like i used to. i don't listen to as much new music all the time as i used to but i still listen to a lot of new stuff, especially pop.
post_survey.habits: i listen to spotify throughout the day when working, both playlists they create and my own playlists. I like to change up genres and discover new and old music. my favorite songs tend to be rock though and/or have heavy guitar influence.
